    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Short, usually double-breasted and belted, coats or jackets made of a thick, woolen, often plaid, material.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
